NAME
  purgelib - removing entries from package.loaded
  
SYNOPSIS
  purgelib libnames...
  
DESCRIPTION
  This program removes entries from the package.loaded table.
  If you are developping a library and are tired of restarting your computer whenever you changed something this might be something for you.
  
EXAMPLES
  purgelib mpm.textgfx
    removes the library mpm.textgfx
